Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.27,0:00:22.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.10,0:00:23.51,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.51,0:00:23.81,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.81,0:00:24.60,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Die, die, die!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:24.60,0:00:26.31,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Die, die, die, die!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.31,0:00:28.41,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave any of your recessive genes behind.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.41,0:00:30.46,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You damned sex addict.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:30.90,0:00:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:32.67,0:00:34.56,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Building Builder?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.56,0:00:35.94,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.86,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Women are so brainless.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.86,0:00:40.24,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Really? But he looks so much like him.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.24,0:00:42.38,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Look at his lips; see how they're so puffy?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:42.38,0:00:46.67,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the only criteria, then even the old guy from Abacus Tutor looks like Building Builder.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:48.25,0:00:50.95,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but Jintan...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:50.95,0:00:52.75,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.97,0:00:56.99,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.13,0:01:02.87,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Summer's beast is fierce indeed.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.87,0:01:06.93,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no fair! I want salty ramen, too!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.75,0:01:09.92,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, an egg!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:09.92,0:01:13.34,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I want egg soup, egg soup!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:17.47,0:01:18.47,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:19.23,0:01:20.38,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,The egg.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:20.83,0:01:22.29,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be lumpy.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.30,0:01:27.24,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Stir the egg, stir it, stir it!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:27.24,0:01:28.71,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Ramen?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.08,0:01:31.70,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That looks good. Make some for me, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:29.07,0:01:30.77,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, it's your dad.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:30.77,0:01:32.73,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thanks for having me over.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:34.81,0:01:35.66,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.50,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:37.50,0:01:39.57,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! How cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:37.50,0:01:41.55,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why are you making it for your dad but not for me?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.57,0:01:42.89,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,How about you quit that habit of calling everything cute?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.89,0:01:46.91,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wow, your dad just said the way I talk is cute! What part is cute, exactly?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.91,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What? But it's such a great word. You can use it in any situation.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:46.91,0:01:48.92,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Except normally you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.92,0:01:49.84,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want an egg in it?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:49.84,0:01:51.02,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Throw one in,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.02,0:01:52.12,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,but don't break it apart.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.12,0:01:53.30,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.13,0:01:55.05,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ah! Even your dad likes it that way!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.05,0:01:57.22,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Favorites, favorites, old people's flavors!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.03,0:01:59.59,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.19,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Time for some TV.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.41,0:02:02.19,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Hey everyone, today...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.19,0:02:03.46,Default,TV,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a cat. How cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:03.88,0:02:06.94,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's acting completely normal.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.30,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,So that must mean...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.94,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jintan!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.75,0:02:12.54,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.82,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:15.25,0:02:17.03,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dig in.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.66,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Pepper, pepper, and more pepper.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.72,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,More pepper... there!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.90,0:02:26.20,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm going to eat too.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.20,0:02:26.87,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.10,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, oh, it's no-
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.96,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chopsticks. Where are the chopsticks?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.96,0:02:33.21,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The chopsticks!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.68,0:02:36.22,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.66,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's wrong with you? Did you get a heatstroke from sitting in the house?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.57,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,That's cute, but that's also serious!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.26,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.90,0:02:49.54,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That summer back then...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.97,0:02:58.90,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.90,0:03:00.32,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.11,0:03:07.16,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Jintan's is the biggest one for sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.87,0:03:08.55,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.64,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's really huge.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.02,0:03:15.01,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan's so cool.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.35,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Who I was back then...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.90,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.01,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.21,0:03:25.10,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Menma?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.36,0:03:30.81,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.52,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I have a wish.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,-OP-
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.32,0:05:15.95,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What happened?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.31,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm sick. Without a doubt.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.98,0:05:30.68,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All of the stress and trauma I've accumulated until now have become corporeal due to the summer heat...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.68,0:05:35.30,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Even my pubescent sexual urges have been thrown into the mix.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.86,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.71,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,For now...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.77,0:05:50.44,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say that you're here as the embodiment of my stress.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.24,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.21,0:05:54.91,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you appear now?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.60,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.80,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,why did you appear as a mature version of yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.99,0:06:05.50,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Ummm... let me think...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.90,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.26,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.50,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.50,0:06:14.81,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I think I want to have my wish come true. That's it!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.61,0:06:18.80,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Your wish? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.90,0:06:21.79,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.79,0:06:23.72,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.59,0:06:27.23,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,How can you get a wish fulfilled when you don't even know what it is?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.21,0:06:31.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But I really do get that feeling that's the reason.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.49,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.75,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:34.33,0:06:37.60,Alt,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Eewww, you spat on me!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.60,0:06:38.87,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.83,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She is the summer beast.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.61,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She is my stress.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She is my trauma.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.25,0:06:49.13,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,For now, just try to remember what your wish was.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.13,0:06:53.86,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, about that! It was a wish that could only come true if everyone was together.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.61,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone? You mean...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.95,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.95,0:07:01.87,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I told you to wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.83,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But someone's at the door.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.90,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if you opened the door?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.19,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Just be quiet and wait...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.87,0:07:12.16,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.87,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's Anaru!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.10,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, calm down!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.10,0:07:21.00,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down? I'm not exactly worked up.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.42,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.99,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like there's a weight on my neck.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.45,0:07:32.56,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru, you can't see me?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.27,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,So what's up?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.18,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.54,0:07:43.12,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher asked me to bring you your homework for summer break.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.12,0:07:47.19,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Now? There are only two days of summer break left you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.19,0:07:50.17,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I have a lot going on.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.68,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should have tossed this away somewhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.65,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't feel like going to that school for retards any more.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.65,0:08:00.90,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care whether you come to school or not.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.94,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,But you should be ashamed of yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.81,0:08:13.69,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:13.69,0:08:14.76,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Ana...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.55,0:08:33.95,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta, you big dummy!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.29,0:08:38.26,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you ask her?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.26,0:08:42.37,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Just say, 'Let's grant her wish together, Anaru!'
Dialogue: 5,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.46,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, don't call her Anaru.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.90,0:08:51.37,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Pick either Anjou or Naruko and stick with it.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.37,0:08:54.29,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I? Anaru is Anaru.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.29,0:08:58.79,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,She's nice to everyone, and has lots of video games and manga.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.79,0:08:59.56,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.20,0:09:04.90,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She's not the Anaru she was back then anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.91,0:09:09.58,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That rotten bitch wouldn't help me even if I asked her.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.06,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,'Rotten bitch?'
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.89,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It means, 'stupid woman.'
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.57,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, she's not my friend anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.57,0:09:16.62,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.45,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.93,0:09:22.67,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it when you say bad things about Anaru.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.30,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.30,0:09:30.00,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go talk to her again! Let's ask her, Jintan!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.56,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.56,0:09:35.01,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Alright already.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.18,0:09:39.67,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've seen Anjou you should \Nunderstand what it means for your wish.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.51,0:09:45.79,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not just Anjou, everything has changed since back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.03,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.34,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.93,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing a hat and glasses?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.93,0:10:03.99,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.65,0:10:05.72,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.10,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.21,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.17,Default,Woman2,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there. Going shopping?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.17,0:10:13.83,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Say, did you hear...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.07,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.54,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.36,0:10:27.46,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.46,0:10:28.60,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.35,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny expression.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.35,0:10:33.10,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you have a piece of green onion from the ramen stuck to your teeth!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.10,0:10:34.07,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.60,0:10:40.50,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.18,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:49.94,0:10:52.96,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru's house isn't this way.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.39,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking a walk since we're outside anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.27,0:11:02.91,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,This used to be Bomu-Bomu! Now it's a WcDonald's!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.91,0:11:05.56,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! But I...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.44,Default,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that one movie?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.34,0:11:07.44,Alt,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys went to my middle school.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.16,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.16,0:11:12.49,Default,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the one with the girl that uses \Nnun-chucks to fight aliens that show up at school.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.40,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.26,Default,Guy1,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't seen it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.11,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Were those your friends?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:21.25,0:11:23.41,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way it is.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.65,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Those grannies really got me worked up,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.65,0:11:28.53,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,but no one gives me a second thought.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.83,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Even Anaru said as much.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.78,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't give a damn about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.80,0:11:36.55,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,'Snap!' goes your neck!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It smells like summer!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.71,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.71,0:11:45.35,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.45,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.33,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really a surprise.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.33,0:11:51.18,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a hallucination, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.11,0:11:57.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,'Please grant my wish,' huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.03,0:12:03.71,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,This must be, without a doubt, because of my relationship with her...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.65,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.87,0:12:07.88,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.26,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? That's dangerous.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.91,0:12:17.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.80,0:12:21.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Menma has...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.92,0:12:38.65,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Ji...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.15,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.79,0:12:43.94,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.00,0:12:46.95,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.61,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:50.61,0:12:51.52,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.52,0:12:57.21,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.85,0:13:25.55,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Naruko.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.09,0:13:27.68,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Did you go to Jin's house?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.73,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Knock first!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.73,0:13:32.01,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I did. Well anyway....
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.01,0:13:36.07,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I only stopped by for a bit. And it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.07,0:13:40.57,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes it is. I wanted you to take them some steamed buns.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.54,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Just take them by yourself!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.54,0:13:45.05,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oho, someones going through puberty.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.95,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.35,0:13:55.41,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,...who should be ashamed.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.00,0:13:57.74,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.51,0:14:00.33,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.16,0:14:03.73,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way home from summer classes.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:03.73,0:14:06.00,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know? We're going to a college-prep high school.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.39,0:14:08.49,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's the high school uniform
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.95,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,that I was going to wear.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.73,0:14:12.04,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.05,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yadomi?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.78,0:14:14.71,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.10,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.64,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.64,0:14:18.85,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Hey...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.79,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,That's Yukiatsu and Tsuruko!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.69,0:14:28.49,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.73,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean, Menma is...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.17,0:14:34.48,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it, I mean...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.48,0:14:35.80,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What about Menma?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.98,0:14:37.94,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.94,0:14:40.55,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still talking about that?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.34,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.34,0:14:44.98,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.46,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.46,0:14:49.25,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently you're not going to school.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.72,0:14:55.35,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You failed the entrance exams and ended up going to a low-tier school around here.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.35,0:14:58.22,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to school, and you're blurting out Meiko Honma's name.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.00,0:15:01.25,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong with your head?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.10,0:15:05.97,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.33,0:15:09.18,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu, you idiot!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.54,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting so worked up over?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.83,0:15:20.52,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Even you change when you talk about Meiko Honma.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.52,0:15:23.40,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Yukiatsu?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.27,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.82,0:15:28.70,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pathetic guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.61,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,But you do have your looks going for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.50,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I also have my brains.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.45,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you do.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.03,0:15:39.05,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.35,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.22,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.31,0:15:53.21,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it now?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.72,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.52,0:16:02.39,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it. The one who's changed the most is me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.39,0:16:03.10,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.80,0:16:04.44,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.44,0:16:09.20,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, my stress. Give me a break already.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.82,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm with you, I remember...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.45,0:16:15.53,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I remember things I don't want to.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.11,0:16:18.65,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,And I get pissed off.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.66,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.27,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.49,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That summer back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.27,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like this.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:48.11,0:16:49.11,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.69,0:16:51.79,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.84,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be the Super Peace Busters!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.65,0:16:57.90,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.63,0:17:00.23,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's 'busters?'
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.33,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a group of strong people.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.87,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,We'll protect the peace!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.87,0:17:06.77,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.77,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,What peace are we going to protect?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.15,0:17:10.15,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,The peace here, there, and everywhere!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.38,0:17:14.01,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Then Jintan will be the leader, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.75,0:17:15.54,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.14,0:17:19.57,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone followed me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.63,0:17:21.49,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.23,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,On that day.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.48,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Even on that day.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.35,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jintan.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.92,0:17:31.81,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.25,0:17:35.39,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You like Menma, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.87,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.42,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.05,0:17:47.67,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any secrets among the Super Peace Busters.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.92,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.92,0:17:51.89,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Say it, say it, say it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.67,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Just let it go already.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.01,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.42,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd like an ugly girl like...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.15,0:18:07.98,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she'd cry.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.70,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Because she's such a crybaby.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:12.43,0:18:13.31,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.92,0:18:21.74,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Jintan!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.74,0:18:23.34,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.57,0:18:29.81,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're back already?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.56,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to see your mom for a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.56,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Microwave the food I left you before you eat it.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.00,0:18:42.99,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That smile tore at my heart.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:45.03,0:18:47.38,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should just apologize tomorrow.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.68,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Gross.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.68,0:18:51.48,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,But that tomorrow...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.60,0:18:55.05,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,...never came.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.54,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Curry.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.49,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,The door's open.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.49,0:19:15.85,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should close it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.85,0:19:20.84,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's Saa! You've gotten so big.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.84,0:19:24.62,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,And dad's got lots of gray hair.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.65,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Mama.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.82,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop doing that already.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.37,0:19:39.40,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Saa?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.12,0:19:42.98,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,You always offer a bowl to Sis whenever we have curry.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:42.98,0:19:44.66,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,It's an eyesore.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.66,0:19:47.93,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's because it was her favorite food.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.80,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Dead people don't eat.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.96,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.50,0:20:00.71,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister was a bit of an airhead, so maybe she hasn't even realized that she died.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.39,0:20:02.44,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.10,0:20:08.99,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I died.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.62,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.97,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. The cup moved on its own.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.97,0:20:17.14,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Menma?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.15,Alt,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Just clean it up.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.15,0:20:20.05,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.47,0:20:24.57,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Completely empty.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.77,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it, dad.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.16,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.22,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,...all of us who busted peace...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.08,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,...just drifted apart.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.35,0:20:52.49,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I want egg soup, egg soup!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.74,0:20:55.99,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,-ED-
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.87,0:21:05.27,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.81,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Where could she have gone?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.87,0:21:18.05,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:19.10,0:21:20.56,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,...the tomorrow after that day...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.25,0:21:24.11,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,...the tomorrow when I could apologize to Menma...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.84,0:21:25.98,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,...to arrive!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.35,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.58,0:21:39.08,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,My stress.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.73,0:21:43.20,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,My trauma.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:51.03,0:21:53.38,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:54.62,0:21:57.66,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I conjured Menma up so that I could apologize to her.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:58.34,0:22:01.04,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then I have to...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:16.39,0:22:17.28,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Men...
Dialogue: 5,0:22:25.20,0:22:26.96,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:30.20,0:22:33.07,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,This is one specific fetish.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:33.07,0:22:33.78,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:33.78,0:22:37.22,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,The romance lies in the impossibility!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:38.46,0:22:40.82,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're Jintan, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:41.65,0:22:42.82,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:44.01,0:22:46.62,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's carve our name here.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:46.62,0:22:48.35,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,How do you write 'super?'
Dialogue: 5,0:22:48.35,0:22:49.55,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't learned it yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:49.55,0:22:52.47,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Write the radical for 'run' to the left...
